{"tid":843750,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【病都要奶共】袁偉豪缺席大陸國慶活動 51秒短片再三向主辦道歉","createTime":"2018-10-01T11:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T12:27:51.000Z","uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"407e9887d759841e721b248243deb2c6c05088b9","tid":843750,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"今日星期一，無啦啦多咗國慶假期，好多人都安排咗活動玩下休息下，藝人們就趁呢個機會工作搵銀。<br />\n<br />\n不過袁偉豪就唔好彩喇，早兩日佢喺ig先貼咗段滑水片段，龍精虎猛咁話要好好建立生活，但到咗今日中午，佢率先喺微博更新微博，同大陸網民say sorry，話因為急性腸胃炎而留醫，唔可以去到大陸一個廣場出席活動。<br />\n<br />\n為咗向大陸網民展示誠意，袁偉豪就算氣若游絲，都拍咗一段51秒嘅片親口道歉，佢仲提咗三次廣場名，feel到佢嗰種無奈同可惜。好多人都留言祝佢早日康復，亦都有人同袁偉豪一樣，抽到活動入場卷原本滿心歡喜，不過見到佢病咗，同佢一樣咁sad喎。袁偉豪回覆傳媒時表示：「寶兒有陪伴我，我一向腸胃都比較一般，睇睇夜晚可唔可以出院啦！有心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181001/58743702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743702&d=wxCBMOCrh%2F4zoxv4IeR4H26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=96d5514a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743702&h=112d85ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181001/58743702</a>"},{"pid":"55ded32460011d49bef998f0882f96d600ff710e","tid":843750,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375920_2bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375920_2bf8.jpg&h=d8d98511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁偉豪急性腸胃炎留醫，佢回覆傳媒時話女友陪伴在側，今晚有機會出得院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375389_b463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375389_b463.jpg&h=09f85e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日就瞓喺病床拍片，為失場道歉，仲剖白內心其實係好想返大陸同fans玩遊戲。（微博截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375389_aa00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375389_aa00.jpg&h=32b20b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢前日先龍精虎猛咁去滑水，可能係「攝」親病咗。（ig圖片）"},{"pid":"ea4aad7672a04e3787ad9a46369c0ad315536a62","tid":843750,"uid":38904,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"人民日報: <br />\n生病是不能出席母親誕辰的原因嗎?"},{"pid":"d5dba00bd2f68fbae17aaf3f6d87d48f98a25d3b","tid":843750,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"完全係怕咗中國班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6fed3f2daecb92f5d8d1e51830edf74ebdac40","tid":843750,"uid":117837,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"ea4aad7672a04e3787ad9a46369c0ad315536a62","tid":843750,"uid":38904,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"人民日報: <br />\n生病是不能出席母親誕辰的原因嗎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"人民日報: 袁偉豪是佔中港獨反共黃絲藝人"},{"pid":"b3b3d5d3658da76b4fd84ad96805243484cd1435","tid":843750,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"奶共狗"},{"pid":"f159d6314622b2297a77c28b5a3e33832b54ea59","tid":843750,"uid":136317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"祖高美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864d0424b69f6ccabe10a3f9aeb863c143d337d2","tid":843750,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"已unfollow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eee9e13ea2f0df6a295b1ea9e7e4416eb89bac","tid":843750,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislik